Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Same medium. Same love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For the ones who made time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chennai still feels like home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweater, laughter, small things that stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Singapore said think bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Plan boldly. Live fully.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Orlando kept the thread alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from far away, still close.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust like this changes everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Be bold. Live a full life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for making it together. Ciao.
